        "en": "Weigh accurately the mass of not less than 20 eluted in this order with the resolution between these peaks being not less than 2.5. System repeatability: When the test is repeated 6 times with 20 mL of the standard solution under the above operat-ing conditions, the relative standard deviation of the ratio of the peak area of diethylcarbamazine to that of the internal standard is not more than 1.0z."
      }
